        <mxCell id="uU0IHdjwgiejwzPI_jMc-12" value="&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: light-dark(rgb(0, 0, 0), rgb(255, 255, 255));&quot;&gt;It is very hard to find any two data blocks `x` and `y` such that: `H (x) = H (y)`&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;hachureGap=4;fontFamily=Mina;strokeWidth=2;fillColor=#90D2D8;strokeColor=#000000;fontSize=16;fontStyle=1;labelBorderColor=none;textShadow=0;labelBackgroundColor=none;align=left;spacing=5;verticalAlign=middle;fillStyle=solid;glass=0;shadow=0;opacity=30;" parent="hOXUQQMBu0Lae1k2kh_e-74" vertex="1">
